Package se.swedenconnect.spring.saml.idp.authnrequest

Interface Saml2ServiceProviderFilter

All Superinterfaces:
Predicate<org.opensaml.saml.saml2.metadata.EntityDescriptor>
public interface Saml2ServiceProviderFilter extends Predicate<org.opensaml.saml.saml2.metadata.EntityDescriptor>
A Predicate that tells whether a SAML Service Provider sending an authentication request is accepted. The predicate will be applied after the request has been fully validated. The primary purpose for the filter is that Identity Providers wishing to restrict its services to only some SP:s within a federation can do so.
